Introduction

Jang Nayoung, known under her stage name Hina, is a South Korean guitarist, keyboardist, Twitch streamer, and cosplayer under 3Y CORPORATION and Tamago Production. She is best known as the guitarist, keyboardist, and the maknae of the project girl band QWER. She represents the letter E.

On August 3, 2023, Hina was confirmed as a member of the upcoming female band QWER. She made her debut with the band on October 18, 2023, with the release of their debut single album, "Harmony from Discord".

Hina discreetly uses a secret Discord account under the username yuki_tei.
